scenes.description: Guest appearance by Ayunda Risu and Kaelia Ela in Anya's 3D room.
Anya thanks her guests and waits for the next arrival.

subtitles.english: Whoa, cool! And next to her is Jamet... wait, no. What's your name? It's not Jamet, right?

subtitles.original: Jamet Jamet... Aku Omet... gak...
subtitles.english: Jamet, Jamet... I'm Omet... no...

subtitles.original: Aku Omet Kaelia Omet.
subtitles.english: I'm Omet, Kaelia Omet.

subtitles.original: Omet dua orang. Omet dua orang ya.
subtitles.english: Omet for two. Omet for two, okay.

subtitles.english: Omet for two, okay. ID Gen 3!

subtitles.english: Whoa, Risu-senpai and Kaelia, thank you so much for coming!

subtitles.english: How do you guys like my room? How is my room, guys?

subtitles.english: Isn't it crazy? Look at that table.

subtitles.english: What for? I want to loot.

subtitles.original: Mau looting... jangan looting aku.
subtitles.english: I want to loot... don't loot me.

subtitles.original: Jangan looting aku, aku dari hobo bisa berusaha sekeras ini...
subtitles.english: Don't loot me. I worked so hard from being a hobo...

subtitles.original: ...untuk dapetin kamar yang sekeren ini. Gila.
subtitles.english: ...to get a room as cool as this. It's crazy.

subtitles.original: Bagi-bagilah... bagi-bagilah.
subtitles.english: Share some... share some.

subtitles.original: Liat deh guys di meja ini aku lumayan banyak senjata ya guys.
subtitles.english: Look guys, on this table I have quite a lot of weapons.

subtitles.english: I've gathered quite a few weapons... anyway, there are many.

subtitles.original: Di situ ada... ada gun... dan ada keris. Oh my god!
subtitles.english: Over there is... a gun... and a keris. Oh my god!

subtitles.original: Just like me for real for real.
subtitles.english: Just like me for real for real.

subtitles.original: Oh my god, but I have something even more cooler.
subtitles.english: Oh my god, but I have something even cooler.

subtitles.original: Aku ada yang lebih keren guys.
subtitles.english: I have something even cooler, guys.

subtitles.original: Wih apa itu? Apa tuh?
subtitles.english: Whoa, what is it? What is it?

subtitles.original: Okay... Jyan!
subtitles.english: Okay... Ta-da!

subtitles.original: Widiih! Apa ini Pai-sen? Ini apa tuh Pai-sen?
subtitles.english: Whoa! What's this, Pai-sen? What is this, Pai-sen?

subtitles.english: That... that is a Magic Dagger!

subtitles.original: Wih gila keren keren... keren keren keren.
subtitles.english: Whoa, crazy cool... cool cool cool.

subtitles.english: ...can I request a pose?

subtitles.original: Oh boleh dong! Let's go! Asik.
subtitles.english: Of course! Let's go! Awesome.

subtitles.original: Mantap! Mantap banget gak sih. Keren banget.

subtitles.english: There's one more by the way. There's one more, guys.

subtitles.english: Oh right, from Kaelia too. What is it?

subtitles.original: Okay bentar aku ambil dulu.

subtitles.original: Jyan! Apa ini? Widiih!

subtitles.english: Sure, sure. What is it?

subtitles.english: Yeah?

subtitles.english: So that was Risu-senpai and Jamet... wait, no, Kaelia.

subtitles.english: Do we have any more guests I wonder?
